import React from "react";
import { Box, Dialog, DialogActions, DialogContent, DialogTitle, IconButton, Typography } from '@material-ui/core'
import {Close as CloseIcon} from '@material-ui/icons'


export default (props) => (
    
    <Dialog open={!!Object.keys(props.job).length} fullWidth>
         <DialogTitle>
            <Box display="flex" justifyContent="space-between" alignItems="center">
            console.log(props);
               {props.job.title} @ {props.job.companyName}
                {/* onClick={closeModal} */}
          <IconButton >
            <CloseIcon />
          </IconButton>
        </Box>
        </DialogTitle>
        <DialogContent>
            <Box>
                <Box display="flex">

                    <Typography variant="caption">Posted On :</Typography>
                    <Typography variant="caption">{ `${props.jobs.postedOn}`}</Typography>
                </Box>
            </Box>
        </DialogContent>
        <DialogActions>

        </DialogActions>
    </Dialog>
)
